      "comment": "HOT RUBY (6) ran below her best last time finishing fifth (31.92) over 530m at this track in a Other. Has an impeccable record at this journey winning all two. Rates on top in this line up. LENNY LIMES (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Murray Bridge behind Diogo Keeping (16.76) in a Grade 6. Has the pace to be prominent. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Hard to beat again. STOP HIM (1) skirted wide from an outside draw last start and found the front, leading throughout to win (30.02) at Gosford in a Mix over 515m. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. KILCOY GEM (4) is always a threat when she races at this journey.",
